Package org.hibernate.search.engine.search.predicate.spi

Interface SearchPredicateBuilderFactory<C>

  • Type Parameters:
    C - The type of query element collector
    public interface SearchPredicateBuilderFactory<C>
    A factory for search predicate builders.

    This is the main entry point for the engine to ask the backend to build search predicates.
